# Dogfood: running mnema against itself for testing.
# Every Mnema-managed artefact lives under .mnema/ in the new layout,
# so a single rule covers the database, audit log, backlog markdowns,
# memory, sprints, etc. AGENTS.md is also touched (init appends a
